at a fire beetle looked like. With a lot difficulty and with the help of a stranger I made it trough the tunnel to Qeynos Hills. There I met the guards and some other young rangers. I saw my first fire beetle and decided to attack him. With a lot of struggle I managed to kill him and got his eye. I thought the fire beetle eye was great. I could see much better in the dark. I believe this was the first time I used that low-level sword.<br><br>I was raised by Hagar Sureshot. He took care of me after both my parents were killed. He has been a good friend and mentor to me. You can often see him at the archery range teaching young rangers. He taught me a lot about combat skills, tracking and fletching. I make it a point to go visit him every few seasons and he always has something new for me to learn.<br><br>I do not remember much about my parents. They both died when I was very young. But Hagar knew them well and he often tells me stories about them. One day he told me how they died. It was during a raid on Vox the dragon. He tells me it was quite amazing to see both of my parents fight together. It was as if their minds were one. During the raid they were part of a bank of rangers strategically located between the casters and the dragon. They were both perfectly synchronized shooting arrow after arrow at the beast. They loaded their bows over and over with godlike speed and grace. Suddenly, the casters started yelling for help. Vox started to attack them. Without saying a word, they put their bows down simultaneously and displayed their dormant blades. They ran to the aid of the casters in the blink of an eye and started slashing at Vox. The dragon was in pain and turned to my parents, allowing the group of casters to evacuate. But now, without the casters the raid had no chance for success. By this time other dragons came to the aid of Vox. Resistance was futile. The rest of the raiding party ran for safety while my parents held back the dragons. My parents never made it. I was told that later scouts were sent in camouflage to retrieve their corpses. But the corpses were not there. It is believed the dragons took it upon themselves to incinerate the remains. With tears running down my face I swore I would avenge my parents’ death. I patiently await this day.<br><br>Watch out Vox, I am coming for you.<br> <p><br><hr><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=221012>Maxvs Wolftracker</a><br>Weilder of Many Weapons<br>Pathfinder of 51 Seassons<br>House of Carnage<br></center><hr></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uaeonii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeonii</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myezboard.com/projects/ezboard/ezboard_userimages/immortalkindred/images/colors.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/19/02 6:17:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2741.topic&index=14>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> deleted</span><hr size=1> deleted <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uaeonii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeonii</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myezboard.com/projects/ezboard/ezboard_userimages/immortalkindred/images/colors.gif" BORDER=0> at: 9/30/02 1:08:09 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=ht