nd that hatred spread to all around him. Innoruuk enjoyed this immensely. Jiren and he came to an &quot;understanding&quot; of sorts. Jiren would make the world hate and fear him, as long as Innoruuk provided the means to do so.. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=korzax>Korzax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 52<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/21/02 5:29:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2741.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Is dat joo?</span><hr size=1> Born in the mountains,<br>Raised in the cave,<br>Blasting n' casting is all I crave.<br><br>nuff sed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 1059<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/21/02 10:02:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2741.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~ Love is for the Weak ~</span><hr size=1> Evil Born.<br>Evil Lived.<br>Evil Done.<br><br>Created from the very hatered of two people. Born from the most Horrific act to be perfomed upon another.<br>Created inbetween the cross between two ancient warring races from times long past.<br><br>A Single Child.<br><br>A Child of Chaos?<br>A Child of Order?<br><br>Neither. A Child of Evil. His Weapon is his Voice. His Blade is his enforcer. Those that stand in the way of the destruction shall die.<br